(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Waves.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind wave properties such as) Tj
T*
(wavelength, frequency, and amplitude.) Tj
T*
